  "text": "where t ox is the SiO 2 liner thickness, V F B the flat band voltage, V is supply voltage, ε ox the dielectric constant of the SiO 2 liner, and N a the silicon doping concentration. We verified the proposed analytical formula by comparing it with the C-V curve obtained from static simulation and measurement with a static bias. The TSV capacitance C TSV (V (t)) is much higher than the capacitance obtained assuming small signal analysis and non-biasing condition [CITATION_1] .",
